<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="pain-n">pain <strong><em>n</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /peɪn/    美 /peɪn/  </p>
<p>[C] &amp; [U]</p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>(肉体上的) 痛；疼痛：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>I <strong>have a pain in my stomach / stomach pains</strong>.
我胃痛。</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>have pain all over 
全身疼痛</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>After a long run, you may feel like you're <strong>in pain</strong>.
在长跑之后，你可能会感到疼痛。</p><footer>2020浙江</footer></div>

<h4 id="2">2.★ <strong>(精神上的) 痛苦；苦恼：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p><strong>cause (sb) pain</strong>
使某人痛苦</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>The parents are still in great pain over the death of their child. 
那对父母仍处于孩子离世带来的痛苦之中。</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>No pain, no gain.
不劳无获。</p></div>

<h2 id="_2">固定搭配</h2>
<h3 id="take-pains-to-do-sth">take pains to do sth</h3>
<p>1.<strong>努力 / 下苦功做某事：</strong>  </p>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>We should take pains to improve ourselves through learning and get prepared for the future.
我们应该通过学习努力改善自己，并为将来作好准备。</p><footer>2015 福建书面表达</footer></div>

<h2 id="_3">派生词汇</h2>
<p>painless /'peɪnləs/ adj   </p></div>